de: Annex A to the Memorandum of Understanding between the Federal Ministry of Defence of the Federal Republic of Germany, the Ministry of Defence of the Kingdom of the Netherlands and the Federal Department of Defence, Civil Protection and Sport of the Swiss Confederation on cooperation in conducting the final exercises of the UN Military Observer Courses of the national UN Training Centres from 24 June 2011 to 29 June 2011  - 21-06-2011 - Verständigungsprotokoll zwischen der Schweiz, Deutschland und den Niederlanden, betreffend die Zusammenarbeit im Rahmen der Schlussübung der UNO Militärbeobachterkurse, 24. - 29.6.2011
en: Annex A to the Memorandum of Understanding between the Federal Ministry of Defence of the Federal Republic of Germany, the Ministry of Defence of the Kingdom of the Netherlands and the Federal Department of Defence, Civil Protection and Sport of the Swiss Confederation on cooperation in conducting the final exercises of the UN Military Observer Courses of the national UN Training Centres from 24 June 2011 to 29 June 2011  - 21-06-2011 - Memorandum of Understanding between the Federal Ministry of Defence of the Federal Republic of Germany, the Ministry of Defence of the Kingdom of the Netherlands and the Federal Department of Defence, Civil Protection and Sport of the Swiss Confederation concerning the Cooperation in Conducting the Final Exercises of the UN Military Observer Courses of the national UN Training Centres (4-PCE-11) from 24 June 2011 to 29 June 2011
fr: Annex A to the Memorandum of Understanding between the Federal Ministry of Defence of the Federal Republic of Germany, the Ministry of Defence of the Kingdom of the Netherlands and the Federal Department of Defence, Civil Protection and Sport of the Swiss Confederation on cooperation in conducting the final exercises of the UN Military Observer Courses of the national UN Training Centres from 24 June 2011 to 29 June 2011  - 21-06-2011 - Protocole d'entente entre la Suisse, l'Allemagne, et les Pays-Bas, concernant la collaboration dans le cadre de l'exercice final des cours des observateurs militaires de l'ONU, 24. - 29.6.2011
